68
00:06:32,940 --> 00:06:40,100
So we've been running citizen juries in Melbourne since 2014.

69
00:06:40,100 --> 00:06:48,600
Nicholas actually sat in on the first one we did for the 10-year financial plan for the city of Melbourne and wrote a lot about that one that we facilitated.

70
00:06:48,600 --> 00:06:51,820
