93
00:08:37,220 --> 00:08:39,460
So you address to the householder.

94
00:08:39,460 --> 00:08:40,880
Yes, address to the householder.

95
00:08:41,620 --> 00:08:42,220
Yeah.

96
00:08:42,220 --> 00:08:50,140
You could use a rate space and then you can address to a person, but then you're missing tenants and you'd have to find some way of picking up tenants.

97
00:08:50,140 --> 00:08:55,160
But there are people who are specialised in doing this, doing that sortition part of it.

